# entry name
@NAME=tabulation hashing
# _A_lgorithm, algo _T_echnique, _D_efinition, _P_roblem, or data _S_tructure
@TYPE=A
# autom basic theory search sort tree graph combin numeric etc. see areas.data
@AREA=search
# the definition
@DEFN=The hash value is the {xor} of values from tables ({arrays})
indexed by characters.
# formal definition or {cross reference} to an entry
@FORML=
$h(c) = \oplus<sup>n</sup><sub>i=1</sub> T<sub>i</sub>[c<sub>i</sub>]$,
where $\oplus$ is the {xor} operation,
T<sub>i</sub> is the i<sup>th</sup> table, and
$c<sub>i</sub>$ is the i<sup>th</sup> character.
